{"tid":1821023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部：無論台灣局勢如何世上只有一個中國","createTime":"2020-01-12T02:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T04:37:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"f8fd50e952135d8e2924a4f2bd71c29cf1d32f21","tid":1821023,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:59:18.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部回應台灣的總統大選。發言人耿爽指，台灣問題是中國內政，無論台灣島內局勢怎樣變化，世界上只有一個中國，台灣是中國一部分的基本事實不會改變。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府堅持一個中國原則，反對台獨，反對「兩個中國」和「一中一台」的立場不會改變，國際社會堅持一個中國原則的普遍共識不會改變。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽指，希望並相信國際社會將繼續堅持一個中國原則，理解和支持中國人民反對台獨分裂活動，爭取完成國家統一的正義事業。"},{"pid":"f1c058e52c6ba9c4091786cf9ccb554221c7a0cb","tid":1821023,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:59:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1247519&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1247519%26csid%3D261_341&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=76dca279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1247519&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"214a50e3f0a6cb6e868e86fd954443f5ad7bf003","tid":1821023,"uid":201656,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"一個<span style=\"color: red;\">中</span>華民<span style=\"color: red;\">國</span>"},{"pid":"8cd5ec0367aa2f6108b3404ba8882c5355f52c8b","tid":1821023,"uid":40267,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:02:07.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八"},{"pid":"26f56499a4590f6464e7368f89dac7106f53bb57","tid":1821023,"uid":153764,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:02:32.000Z","msg":"建國得70年就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地百幾年呀"},{"pid":"18d873a0a2ec0b7bfc13da2666fc4c79085a6fe7","tid":1821023,"uid":224916,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-